Theorem int_exp_num:
  (i:int) ** n =
  if 0 ≤ i then &(Num i ** n)
  else if EVEN n then &(Num (-i) ** n)
  else -&(Num (-i) ** n)
Proof
  Cases_on`i` \\ simp[integerTheory.INT_POW_NEG]
QED

